ve-text">Post navigation</h3> <span class="nav-previous"><a href="http://www.gbopera.it/2016/03/opera-di-firenze-saimir-pirgu-il-mio-canto/" rel="prev"><span class="meta-nav">&larr;</span> Opera di Firenze: Saimir Pirgu &#8220;Il mio canto&#8221;</a></span> <span class="nav-next"><a href="http://www.gbopera.it/2016/03/venezia-teatro-la-fenice-omer-meir-wellber-alessandro-marchetti/" rel="next">Venezia, Teatro La Fenice: Omer Meir Wellber &#038; Alessandro Marchetti <span class="meta-nav">&rarr;</span></a></span> </nav><nav class="nav-single-hidden"> <span class="nav-previous"></span> <span class="nav-next"></span><div class="clear"></div> </nav></div><div class="comments-block box-shadow-2px clearfix"><div id="comments" class="comments-area"></div></div></div></div><div id="secondary" class="widget-area span4 sb-4" role="complementary"> <aside id="search-4" class="widget widget_search clearfix"><h3 class="widget-title">RICERCA</h3><form method="get" id="searchform" action="http://www.gbopera.it/"> <label for="s" class="assistive-text">Search</label> <input type="text" class="field" name="s" id="s" placeholder="Search" /> <button type="submit" class="submit btn" name="submit" id="searchsubmit"><i class="icon-search"></i></button></form> </aside><aside id="ct-relatedposts-widget-2" class="widget ct-relatedposts-widget clearfix"><h3 class="widget-title">Articoli correlati</h3><ul class="related-posts-single clearfix"><li> <a href=\'http://www.gbopera.it/2016/07/martina-franca-42-festival-della-valle-ditria-la-grotta-di-trofonio/\' title=\'Martina Franca, 42 Festival della Valle d&#8217;Itria: &#8220;La grotta di Trofonio&#8221;\'><img width="70" height="70" src="http://www.gbopera.it/wp-content/uploads/2016/07/1K8A1319-70x70.jpg" class="attachment-thumbnail size-thumbnail wp-post-image" alt="la grotta di Trofonio, Martina Franca 2016" title="Martina Franca, 42 Festival della Valle d&#8217;Itria: &#8220;La grotta di Trofonio&#8221;" srcset="http://www.gbopera.it/wp-cont